Key take aways from Workshop on Resume Building with TWS mentored by Shubham Londhe:

• Do not use your picture in your resume as it leads to categorical rejection by ATS.

• Do not use even a shred of AI in your resume.

• Avoid Keyword Stuffing.

• For fresher, resume should be of 1 page, for experienced, resume can be of 1-2 pages.

• Do not lie about experience experience, be truthful.

• Use Harvard Resume Template, avoid resume makers like novoresume, canva etc

These are just key points, if you need detailed help with resume making, I am ready to assist with it.
